response.original_title: UFC Fight Night: Blanchfield vs. Barber
response.overview: UFC on ESPN: Blanchfield vs. Barber (also known as UFC on ESPN 68 and UFC Vegas 107 and UFC on ESPN+ 115) is an upcoming mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that will take place on May 31, 2025, at the UFC Apex in Enterprise, Nevada, part of the Las Vegas Valley, United States.
